window.bookSummaryJSON = "A Newbery Honor Book and a Book Sense 76 Selection, <i>Enchantress from the Stars</i> is a science-fiction classic. Three alien races meet on the small green world of Andrecia. The Imperial Exploration Corps wants to claim the planet for its own, but the Anthropological Service stands in the way. And when young Elana makes contact with native Georyn, a love story exploring the very depths of human emotion unfolds."; 
